&lt;h3 id=&quot;japanese&quot;&gt;Japanese&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://i.imgur.com/yRaeWVH.png&quot; alt=&quot;Japanese&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
